{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/ideas/app-ideas-from-twitter-folks","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"goal-manager\" style=\"position:relative;\">Goal manager<a href=\"#goal-manager\" aria-label=\"goal manager permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>A goal manager, where you can set goals with deadlines and different counters, attach habits to that goals, add sub-goals and steps to achieve bigger goals and so on.</p>\n<p>If you make such app, please <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/fromaline/status/1488919113493889026\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">inform Nick</a> about it</p>\n<h2 id=\"twitter-dms\" style=\"position:relative;\">Twitter DMs<a href=\"#twitter-dms\" aria-label=\"twitter dms permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>A Twitter DM &#x3C;-> Email service  to be able to manage my DMs in my HEY inbox.</p>\n<p>Bigger idea would be a plug and play service that allows Email, Slack, Trello etc.</p>\n<p>IF you make such app, please <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/joemasilotti/status/1479094606801162241\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">notify Joe</a> and compare with this <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/jro7/status/1479215037382377477\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">guy</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"appointment-manager\" style=\"position:relative;\">Appointment manager<a href=\"#appointment-manager\" aria-label=\"appointment manager permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Calendly + Wordle.</p>\n<p>You can only make an appointment with me if you can solve this word puzzle in less than 6 tries. If you fail, you have to wait 24 hours before you can reattempt to schedule a meeting with me.</p>\n<p><strong>Author</strong>: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thewmh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">William H</a></p>","excerpt":"Goal manager A goal manager, where you can set goals with deadlines and different counters, attach habits to that goals, add sub-goals and…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#goal-manager\">Goal manager</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#twitter-dms\">Twitter DMs</a></li